description:
***** For a limited time only ******
   * Use this app for converting one unit to another unit.
     * This application is suitable for all Engineering graduates.
     * This application is providing the user friendly interface, So that you can make the conversions quick & easy.
     * You can convert anything to anything quickly while anywhere.
     * This app will support more than 900 conversions.
     * This app will provide you to do quickly and easy translate different units of measure.
* This application supports the following categories of conversions.
o Acceleration 
o Acceleration-angular 
o Data Transfer 
o Density 
o Moment of Force 
o Moment of Inertia 
o Prefix
o Sound 
o Specific Volume 
o Temperature 
o Torque 
o Velocity-angular 
o Frequency Wavelength 
o Fuel Consumption 
o Angle 
o Area 
o Capacity and Volume 
o Data Storage 
o Distance and Length 
o Energy and Work 
o Force 
o Power 
o Pressure 
o Time 
o Velocity 
o Volume-Dry
